##If you’re a leader or potential leader in your field

You may be eligible for the [Global Talent visa](https://www.gov.uk/global-talent-researcher-academic) if you are a leader or potential leader in science, medicine, engineering or humanities.

With this visa, you:

+ may be able to work in the UK without a job offer
+ can be an employee, self-employed and a director of a company

###Eligibility

The eligibility criteria include proving you are a leader or potential leader in your field by applying for an ‘endorsement’.

There are no English language or minimum salary eligibility requirements.

###How long you can stay

Your visa can last for up to 5 years.  You can extend it as long as you're still eligible.

After 3 years, you may be able to settle permanently in the UK.
